Interface PushControlI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ComponentServiceI, OfferedI, PushControlImplementationI, java.rmi.Remote, RequiredI
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PushControlConnector, PushControlInboundPort, PushControlOutboundPort

    public interface PushControlI
extends PushControlImplementationI, OfferedI, RequiredI
    The interface PushingControlI proposes basic component services to control the regular exchanges of data via a DataOfferedI interface in push mode.

    Description

    The interface simply adds to PushControlImplementationI the OfferedI and RequiredI to make it a component interface.
